    bf:tableOfContents [ a bf:TableOfContents ;
            rdfs:label "Evolutionary roots of fungi. The protistan origins of animals and fungi / Martin Carr, Kayleigh Hopkins, and Michael L. Ginger ; Evolution of signalling and morphogenesis in the dictyostelids / Christina Schilde ; The evolution of mitochondrial genomes in fungi / Vassili N. Kouvelis, Alexandra M. Kortsinoglou, and Timothy Y. James -- Evolution of pathogenic strategies. Dimorphism and pathogenesis in Mucor species / Alexis Garcia, Courtney P. Smith, and Soo Chan Lee ; Genome evolution in fungal plant pathogens : from populations to kingdom-wide dynamics / Ursula Oggenfuss, Alice Feurtey, Claudia Sarai Reyes-Avila, Emile Gluck-Thaler, Guido Puccetti, Hanna Maren Glad, Leen Nanchira Abraham, Luzia Stalder, Sabina Moser Tralamazza, Sandra Milena González-Sáyer, and Daniel Croll ; Host switching and geographic expansions in (hemi)biotrophic plant pathogens / Marco Thines, Hanno Seebens, M. Catherine Aime, Roger G. Shivas, Levente Kiss, Franz Essl, and Anna Schertler -- Evolution of mutualistic interactions. Mycoviruses / Jillian M. Myers and Timothy Y. James ; Bacterial endosymbionts of mucoromycota fungi : diversity and function of their interactions / Jessie K. Uehling, Alessandra Salvioli, Kevin R. Amses, Laila P. Partida-Martínez, Gregory Bonito, and Paola Bonfante ; Fungi and their environmental micropredators / Silvia Radosa, Nauman Saeed, and Falk Hillmann ; Global fungal diversity estimated from high-throughput sequencing / Petr Baldrian, Petr Kohout, and Tomáš Větrovský -- Evolution of metabolism and development. Activation of secondary metabolite production in fungi / Lukas M. Zehner, Mario K.C. Krespach, Maria C. Stroe, Maira Rosin, Volker Schroeckh, and Axel A. Brakhage ; Evolution and diversity of bioluminescent fungi / Huei-Mien Ke, Min R. Lu, Chiung-Chih Chang, Chen Hsiao, Jie-Hao Ou, Yuichi Taneyama, and Isheng Jason Tsai ; Paedomorphosis and evolution of sequestrate basidiomycetes / Francisco Kuhar, Eduardo Nouhra, Donald H. Pfister, and Matthew E. Smith." ] ;
    bf:title [ a bf:Title ;
            rdfs:label "Evolution of fungi and fungal-like organisms /" ;
            bflc:nonSortNum "0" ;
            bf:mainTitle "Evolution of fungi and fungal-like organisms /" ] .

